            <h2 class="section-title">Our clients</h2>
            <a class="btn to-all-reviews" href="#" title="Посмотреть все отзывы">All reviews</a>
            <div class="reviews-list clearfix">
                <blockquote class="review-item">
                    <p>The best food you will find in this area! My husband is from Pittsburgh which has an abundance of restaurants and he would still prefer to come home and eat here instead! Everything is delicious.</p>
